<paragraph id="8BAAE11B352AFFE5FF47F8F4FAE9FF05" blockId="9.[151,1437,1437,2040]" lastBlockId="10.[151,1437,151,357]" lastPageId="10" lastPageNumber="366" pageId="9" pageNumber="365">
<emphasis id="B9613D09352AFFE6FF47F8F4FE4EF8E3" bold="true" box="[199,481,1797,1824]" pageId="9" pageNumber="365">Female. (ICN-Ar 8324).</emphasis>
Total length 6.00. Carapace brown with a medial yellow arrow-shaped mark and two yellow posterolateral stripes, 2.33 long, 1.78 wide, 1.24 high (
<figureCitation id="132EFD9E352AFFE6FCDBF8DBFC1FF8B8" box="[859,944,1833,1860]" captionStart="FIGURES 32–33" captionStartId="9.[151,264,1095,1119]" captionTargetBox="[162,1431,194,1060]" captionTargetId="figure-22@9.[151,1435,181,1071]" captionTargetPageId="9" captionText="FIGURES 32–33. L. lorax Maddison, male (ICN-Ar 8324), 32 habitus; female (ICN-Ar 8324); 33 habitus. Scale bars = 1.00 mm (32–33)." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6501142" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6501142/files/figure.png" pageId="9" pageNumber="365">Fig. 33</figureCitation>
). OC brown with eyes on dark marks, 1.06 long. Anterior eye row 1.67 wide and posterior 1.54 wide. Sternum brown, 0.95 long, 0.76 wide. Labium brown, 0.34 long, 0.39 wide. Chelicerae brown, with two retromarginal and three promarginal teeth. Leg formula: 4132, all yellow with dark brown marks. Leg macrosetae: femur, I–II p 1 di; 
<collectionCode id="ED0479DE352AFFE6FC0AF864FC09F84C" box="[906,934,1942,1968]" pageId="9" pageNumber="365">III</collectionCode>
p 1 di, d 1 di; IV p 1 di, d 2 di; patella, II p 1 me; 
<collectionCode id="ED0479DE352AFFE6FF48F848FF4BF828" box="[200,228,1978,2004]" pageId="9" pageNumber="365">III</collectionCode>
–IV p 1 me, r 1 me; tibia, I v 2–2–2, p 1 di; II v 1–2–2, p 1–1; 
<collectionCode id="ED0479DE352AFFE6FC12F848FC01F828" box="[914,942,1978,2004]" pageId="9" pageNumber="365">III</collectionCode>
v 1–0–2, p 1–1, r 1–1; IV v 1–0–1, p 1–0–1, r 1–0–1; metatarsus, I–II v 2–2, p 1–1; 
<collectionCode id="ED0479DE352AFFE6FDD4F82CFDDFF804" box="[596,624,2014,2040]" pageId="9" pageNumber="365">III</collectionCode>
v 2–0–2, p 1–1–2, r 1–1–2; IV v 1–1–2, p 1–1–1, r 1–1–1–2. Abdomen dark brown with some dispersed yellow spots (
<figureCitation id="132EFD9E3529FFE5FD24FF65FD58FF4D" box="[676,759,151,177]" captionStart="FIGURES 32–33" captionStartId="9.[151,264,1095,1119]" captionTargetBox="[162,1431,194,1060]" captionTargetId="figure-22@9.[151,1435,181,1071]" captionTargetPageId="9" captionText="FIGURES 32–33. L. lorax Maddison, male (ICN-Ar 8324), 32 habitus; female (ICN-Ar 8324); 33 habitus. Scale bars = 1.00 mm (32–33)." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6501142" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6501142/files/figure.png" pageId="10" pageNumber="366">Fig. 33</figureCitation>
). Epigynum (
<figureCitation id="132EFD9E3529FFE5FC0EFF65FBA1FF4E" box="[910,1038,151,178]" captionStart="FIGURES 34–39" captionStartId="10.[151,264,1323,1347]" captionTargetBox="[155,1422,382,1294]" captionTargetId="figure-102@10.[151,1436,381,1299]" captionTargetPageId="10" captionText="FIGURES 34–39. L. lorax Maddison, male (ICN-Ar 8324), 34 male palp, ventral view; 35 same, retrolateral view; female (ICN- Ar 8324), 36, 39 epigynum, cleared, dorsal view; 37 same, lateral view; 38 same, ventral view. Abbreviations: cd=copulatory duct, dTa= dorsal tibial apophysis, e=embolus sp=spermatheca. Scale bars = 0.50 mm (34–35), 0.25 mm (36–39)." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6501144" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6501144/files/figure.png" pageId="10" pageNumber="366">Figs 36–39</figureCitation>
) with copulatory openings (co) in a single anterior oval cavity, overhanging lobe that exceed the posterior margin of the epigynal plate and arises in the upper side of the cavity, short copulatory ducts (cd) and semirounded spermathecae (sp) placed posteriorly.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C30FB2903529FFE5FF47FEF0FB87FEE1" box="[199,1064,258,286]" pageId="10" pageNumber="366" type="description">
<paragraph id="8BAAE11B3529FFE5FF47FEF0FB87FEE1" blockId="10.[151,1437,151,357]" box="[199,1064,258,286]" pageId="10" pageNumber="366">
