(n= 
<specimenCount id="9D132A923529FFE5FEEDFEF1FE74FEE2" box="[365,475,259,286]" pageId="10" pageNumber="366" type="female">2 females</specimenCount>
) Total length 6.00–3.60. Carapace length 2.33–1.77.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
