<figureCitation id="132EFD9E3529FFE5FF20FEB9FF5BFE99" box="[160,244,330,357]" captionStart="FIGURE 57" captionStartId="15.[151,250,1890,1914]" captionTargetBox="[164,1423,181,1866]" captionTargetId="figure-22@15.[164,1423,181,1866]" captionTargetPageId="15" captionText="FIGURE 57. Distribution of jumping spiders of the tribe Lapsiini Maddison (Salticidae: Spartaeinae) in South America. The figures with a dot inside represent the type species of each genus." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6501154" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6501154/files/figure.png" pageId="10" pageNumber="366">Fig. 57</figureCitation>
